metadata.name: Urban Sunset
metadata.description:
A stunning view of a city at sunset, taken from a high vantage point atop a hill. The ultra-wide-angle lens used to capture the scene allows for a sweeping panoramic view, showcasing the entire cityscape with incredible detail. The city is dotted with tall buildings, with a few trees providing a pop of greenery amidst the urban landscape. In the distance, the hills and the sea can be seen, adding depth and dimension to the photo. 
Photo combined with AI and edited in Lightroom and Photoshop.
